Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.67,0:55:56.40,1080P电影中字,,0,0,0,,在調查波特的時候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs40}During the Porter investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.40,0:56:00.24,1080P电影中字,,0,0,0,,他真的借用了神的力量對《環球報》進行壓制\N{\3c&H000000&\fs40}he literally called down the power of god on the globe.
