Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.20,0:58:46.30,1080P电影中字,,0,0,0,,吉姆 你說你幫了巴雷特神父當是人情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs40}Jim, you said you helped out on father Barrett as a favor.
