Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.30,1:36:33.27,1080P电影中字,,0,0,0,,他越級了 我是說 加蘭特是什麼時候寫的信\N{\3c&H000000&\fs40}He broke ranks. I mean, when did Gallant write her letter?
